cs.CL, cs.SI, cs.SD, cs.LG, cs.IR 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper is about natural language processing and word representations. 
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is also likely as the paper uses social network data to train personalized word vectors. 
- cs.SD (Sound) and cs.LG (Learning) are less likely but still possible categories as the paper discusses the use of a machine learning model to learn personalized word vectors. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is also a possible category as the paper evaluates the quality of the personalized word vectors on two application tasks.
